        "subject": "FF-115 daos: DAOS event queue",
        "message": "FF-115 daos: DAOS event queue\n\nAll DAOS operations that cannot complete immediately return after\ninitiating the operation and post an event to an event queue to signal\ncompletion asynchronously.\nThis patch is implementation of DAOS event queue (EQ) and event in\nkernel space, userspace library will be implemented in upcoming patch.\n\nThis patch also includes implementation of DAOS handle table which is\nbased cfs_hash.\n\nSigned-off-by: Liang Zhen <liang.zhen@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I3e1185936fec711821854740db3f0d67ce5a2faa\n"
